io.spine.server.log

Interface LoggingEntity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    io.spine.logging.Logging

    public interface LoggingEntity
extends io.spine.logging.Logging
    A Logging trait for entities.

    When adding logs in an entity, use this interface over Logging.

      • at

        com.google.common.flogger.FluentLogger.Api at(java.util.logging.Level level)
        Creates a FluentLogger.Api with the given level.
        Parameters:
        level - the log level
        Returns:
        new fluent logging API
        API Note:
        This method mirrors the declaration of AbstractEntity.at(Level). When a concrete entity implements this interface, the underscore logging methods will have the same behaviour regarding the log site as does the AbstractEntity.at(Level) method.
